# SURU IOC Feed — Zeek Intelligence Framework format
# Reference: https://docs.zeek.org/en/master/frameworks/intel.html
# MITRE ATT&CK: TA0011 C2 — T1071, T1568
#
# Add entries below. Format:
# <value>\t<Intel::DOMAIN|Intel::ADDR|Intel::FILE_HASH>\tSURU\t<desc>\t-\tT
